{
  "script_id": "parabola-optics",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "你有没有想过，探照灯里一个小小的灯泡，怎么就能射出笔直的一束强光？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "卫星天线又是怎么把散射的微弱信号，牢牢收拢到一个接收头上的？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "答案藏在一条我们很熟悉的曲线里，它就是抛物线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "抛物线有一个精确的定义：到一个定点的距离，永远等于到一条定直线的距离。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "这个定点叫焦点，这条定直线叫准线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.21,
      "size": 51408,
      "text": "对于标准抛物线 x 的平方等于四 p 乘 y，焦点在 y 轴上的 p 处，准线是水平线 y 等于负 p。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "reflect",
      "line_id": "refl-1",
      "filename": "reflect-refl-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/reflect-refl-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "现在让一束平行于对称轴的光，竖直射向这条抛物线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "reflect",
      "line_id": "refl-2",
      "filename": "reflect-refl-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/reflect-refl-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.43,
      "size": 54864,
      "text": "按照反射定律，每条光线打到曲面后都会弹开。神奇的是，它们全都精确地穿过同一个点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "reflect",
      "line_id": "refl-3",
      "filename": "reflect-refl-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/reflect-refl-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.88,
      "size": 46080,
      "text": "这个点，正是焦点。无论光线从哪里射入，反射后都会汇聚到焦点上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "why",
      "line_id": "why-1",
      "filename": "why-why-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/why-why-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.1,
      "size": 49680,
      "text": "奥秘在于抛物线每一点的切线角度，恰好让入射角等于反射角时，反射线都指向焦点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "why",
      "line_id": "why-2",
      "filename": "why-why-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/why-why-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.08,
      "size": 49248,
      "text": "把这个过程反过来，把灯泡放在焦点上，射出的光反射后就变成一束平行光，这就是探照灯。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42336,
      "text": "调节焦准距 p，抛物线开口会变宽或变窄，焦点的高低也随之改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.44,
      "size": 39024,
      "text": "但你会发现，不管开口怎么变，所有平行光始终稳稳地聚在焦点上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "抛物线由焦点和准线定义，曲线上每点到两者的距离相等。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "它的反射性质让平行光聚焦到焦点，也让焦点的光射出平行光。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "parabola-optics",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/parabola-optics/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "从探照灯到卫星天线，一条曲线连接了数学与生活，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 40.48,
  "total_size": 647712
}